Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:05.25,Signs_BText,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(503,493)\pos(320,282)}{This is a work of fiction. The names of the people, places, and organizations\Nare fictitious and in no way related to any real person or entity.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:15.36,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{It's so peaceful.}Yên bình quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:19.61,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{I hope these days continue forever.}Mình ước ngày nào cũng sẽ như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:22.57,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Anyway, back to class.}Thôi, tập trung học nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:34.65,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Well, that peace sure didn't last.}Yên bình... ngắn ngủi quá đi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.08,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{The hell is that?! A nose bubble?}Cái quái gì vậy? Bong bóng mũi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:19.82,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{No, an antler bubble?!}Không, bong bóng nai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:27.41,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{A fairytale scene... but only visually!}Một khung cảnh thần tiên... về mặt hình ảnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:34.36,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Why do you sound like that in your sleep?}Cậu ta nói mớ gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:39.22,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Or rather, don't fall asleep during class. \NEspecially this boldly.}Cơ mà đang trong giờ học đấy,\N ai cho ngủ chứ... Lại còn nổi bật nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:50.13,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{As the class rep, student council president, \Nand this deer's caretaker,}Với tư cách lớp trưởng, hội trưởng và người chăm sóc nai,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:51.31,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{I should probably wake her up.}mình phải đánh thức cậu ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.44,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Hey, Shikanoko. Wake up.}Shikanoko, dậy đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.07,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{And she's not waking up.}Không thèm dậy luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:01.66,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Shikanoko! Hey, Shikanoko!}Shikanoko! Này, Shikanoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.41,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Wake—}Dậy--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.28,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Wha?}Cái quái?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:10.16,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{Reflexes so sharp, you wonder \Nif she's really asleep at all.}Phản xạ nhạy bén đến \Nmức tự hỏi là có ngủ thật không.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:21.38,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Is she rowing a boat now?}Cậu ta đang chèo thuyền à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:27.32,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Well, I mean, I can understand \Ngetting sleepy during last period.}Mà thôi, tiết cuối ai chả buồn ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:28.77,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.52,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{A bird?!}Chim?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:34.90,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Followed by more!}Lại còn tăng thêm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.15,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{And she hasn't noticed at all!}Và không nhận ra luôn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:41.15,Signs_BText,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(320,32)}{10 Minutes Later}10 phút sau
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:41.15,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{Ten minutes later.}Mười phút sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:45.34,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Okay, wake up already!}Dậy mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:47.49,Default,Ukai,0,0,0,,{Koshi-san? What's the matter?}Koshi? Sao thế em?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.97,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Er, it's nothing.}Dạ không...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:53.58,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{Some things have to be called out, \Neven in the middle of class.}Dù trong tiết học, vẫn có những chuyện cần phải nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:57.45,Default,Ukai,0,0,0,,{And then an adjective gets added here...}Và thêm tính từ vào...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.38,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{It's a little late to be asking now, but...}Có hơi trễ để hỏi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:05.89,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Why is no one saying a damn thing \Nabout all of this?!}Nhưng sao chẳng ai quan tâm hết vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:09.26,DefaultTop,Sparrow,0,0,0,,{Jab, jab. Jab, jab.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:10.27,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{Just }{\i0}{My Deer Friend Nokotan}{\i1}{ Things.}Chỉ là một ngày bình thường của Shikanoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:13.89,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{She's seriously not waking up at all. \NIt's messed up!}Không thèm tỉnh luôn. Lạ thật đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:17.35,Default,Ukai,0,0,0,,{Let's see... Who should we have \Ntranslate this sentence into Japanese?}Vậy thì... em nào dịch câu này qua tiếng Nhật xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:22.92,Default,Ukai,0,0,0,,{Well, today's the 12th, so the person \Nwho's attendance number 12!}Hôm nay là ngày 12, mời em số thứ tự 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:24.70,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Crap!}Chết!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:24.11,Signs_BText,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\fs26\pos(130,0)}{Number 12}12
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:24.70,Signs_BText,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\fs26\pos(130,0)}{Number 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.16,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Hey, Shikanoko!}Shikanoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:31.18,Signs,SFX,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,535)\bord2.5\fnArial Black\c&H1E1F34&\3c&HF0F2F0&\pos(320,180)}{Psssssszzzzzzzzz}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.55,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{She's gonna call on you!}Cô gọi kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.79,Default,Ukai,0,0,0,,{Let's see. Number 12 is...}Số 12 là...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:37.33,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,Shikanoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.84,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Your tag's still on.}Nhãn vẫn còn dính kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:52.45,Default,Ukai,0,0,0,,{No way! Oh, no! I forgot to cut the tag off!}Chết! Cô quên cắt nhãn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:55.20,Default,Student A,0,0,0,,{Wait, my tag's not still on, is it?!}Khoan, em cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:57.17,Default,Boy B,0,0,0,,{Hey, who was that just now?}Này, vừa rồi là ai vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.06,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{And she's still asleep!}Và vẫn ngủ được.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:04.45,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Could you not say such \Nstress-inducing things in your sleep?!}Đừng có nói mấy chuyện căng thẳng trong lúc ngủ nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:09.02,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{You can bet Class 3-B didn't \Nget any work done after that.}Sau đó thì lớp 3-B không\N phải làm bất cứ bài tập nào nữa.
