Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:09.33,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{The fierce battle continued \Neven after midnight.}Trận chiến vẫn tiếp tục dù là nửa đêm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.91,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{"But the Day of the Deer \Nis over now, isn't it?"}"Nhưng ngày của nai kết thúc rồi còn gì?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.71,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{No basic jokes like that here.}Không có trò đùa nào ở đây cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.18,DefaultItalics,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Take that.}Ném.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.72,DefaultItalics,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Steppy, steppy, steppy, step.}Chạy chạy chạy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:46.70,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{This was a battle with everything on the line.}Trận chiến đặt cược mọi thứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:14.14,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,{Seems I've finally tracked you down, Noko-san.}Có vẻ ta đã đuổi kịp ngươi rồi, Noko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.15,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs32\fsp1\pos(320,69)}{NOKOTAN'S IN DIRE STRAITS}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.15,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{Nokotan's in dire straits!}Nokotan trong tình huống tuyệt vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.52,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,Shikanoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:22.44,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{You guys are still at it?!}Vẫn còn chơi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.57,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,Koshitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.41,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Witness how our battle ends!}Đây sẽ là kết thúc trận chiến.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:28.53,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:29.93,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,Ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:36.64,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{I will never fall to you! \NBring it, Kumatori Soichiro!}Sẽ không bao giờ thua ngươi, Kumatori Soichiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.80,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{The hell is that weapon?! \NIt looks super inconvenient to use!}Cái vũ khí quái gì vậy? Nhìn thấy khó xài quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.85,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{And what is this mystery dimension?!}Sao lại chuyển qua không gian khác vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:57.10,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,{Oho... At least you're a lively one.}Ô... ngươi có vẻ tự tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:01.48,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,{But you won't be talking like that for long...}Nhưng sẽ không được lâu đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.28,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,Shikanoko Noko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.80,Signs,Kumatori/Subs,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,258)}This is my rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:19.43,Signs,Kumatori/Subs,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,220)}There are many like it, but this one is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:24.44,Signs,Kumatori/Subs,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,228)}My rifle is my best friend. It is my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.44,Signs,Kumatori/Subs,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,258)}I must master it as
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:30.78,Signs,Kumatori/Subs,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,258)}I must master my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.58,Signs,Kumatori/Subs,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,258)}My rifle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:37.75,Signs,Kumatori/Subs,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,258)}and myself are the defenders of my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:41.65,Signs,Kumatori/Subs,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,258)}We are the masters of our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:45.30,Signs,Kumatori/Subs,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,258)}We are the saviors of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.45,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,Your life is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.83,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,Shikanoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:01.00,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,{Oh, time out for a sec.}Khoan đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:05.85,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,{H-Hello—}X-Xin chào--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:08.34,DefaultItalics,Wife,0,0,0,,{Hey! Where the hell are you?!}Ông đang ở đâu thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.68,DefaultItalics,Wife,0,0,0,,{Hurry up and buy the daikon radish \NI asked for and head home!}Nhanh mua củ cải và về nhà đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:12.34,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,{Darlin', I'm sorry—}Bà à, tôi xin lỗi--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:13.82,DefaultItalics,Wife,0,0,0,,{Where are you right now?!}Ông đang ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.12,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,{I'm in Hino right now...}Tôi đang ở Hino...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.67,DefaultItalics,Wife,0,0,0,,{Where the hell's Hino?! In Douou?!}Hino? Douou á?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:21.35,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,{No, uh... Tokyo.}Không... Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:25.34,DefaultItalics,Wife,0,0,0,,{What?! There ain't no Hino in the 23 wards!}Làm quái gì có Hino nào ở Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:28.70,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,{There's a place called \Nthe Tama region in Tokyo.}Có một nơi gọi là khu vực Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:31.36,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,{I'll buy some Nerima daikon and head home.}Tôi sẽ mua củ cải Nerima và đi về.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:34.73,DefaultItalics,Wife,0,0,0,,{How many hours do you think it'll take you \Nto get from Nerima to Nemuro, huh?!}Ông nghĩ tốn bao lâu để đi từ Nerima đến Nemuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:38.75,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Did... Did he go home?}O-Ông ta về nhà rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:43.58,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{This is what friendship, effort, \Nand victory look like!}Đây là tình bạn, nỗ lực và giành chiến thắng!
