Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:47.38,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fnTimes New Roman\c&H0C111C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\pos(564,160)}{Effort}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:47.38,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fnTimes New Roman\c&H0C111C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\pos(91.5,160)}{Victory}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.69,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I don't think you'll be \Nstanding shoulder-to-shoulder}Tớ không nghĩ cậu được sánh vai
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:47.38,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{with a Jump protag anytime soon.}cùng nhân vật chính trong Jump đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:51.14,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{All right! I'm gonna win the next \NDay of the Deer, too!}Ngon! Lần sau bé giành chiến thắng!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:52.55,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{He's gonna be coming by every month?!}Tháng nào lão ta cũng đến à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:57.81,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{The thought of every fourth Tuesday awaiting \Nher plunged Koshitan into a deep despair.}Nghĩ đến ngày thứ 3 tuần thứ 4 làm Koshitan tuyệt vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.99,Default,Cop A,0,0,0,,{What's that on your shoulder?}Vai ông mang gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.44,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,{Huh? Oh!}Hả? A!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:05.14,Default,Kumatori,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sort of in a hurry...}T-Ta đang bận lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:06.70,Default,Cop A,0,0,0,,{You'll be coming to the station with us.}Bận gì cũng về đồn đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:09.34,Default,Cop B,0,0,0,,{Hey, this is a real gun!}Này, súng thật à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:10.32,Default,Cop A,0,0,0,,{What?!}Hả?
