Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:53.24,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Let's do our best in the \NDeer Club again today!}Hôm nay cũng cố gắng hết sức nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.28,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Why are you wearing a tracksuit?}Sao lại mặc đồng phục thể dục?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:58.24,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Oh, I just sent my uniform to the cleaners.}À, đồng phục kia bé giặt rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.20,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{It's all ripped.}Mà sao rách rưới vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:07.75,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Look, over there, too.}Cơ mà ở kia nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:12.21,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,221)\an9\fnTimes New Roman\fs20\c&H250A86&\3c&H58B4DE&\bord2\pos(153.5,162)}{D}{\3c&HF9FBFF&}{e}{\3c&H58B4DE&}{e}{\3c&HF9FBFF&}{r\N}{\3c&H58B4DE&}{C}{\3c&HF9FBFF&}{r}{\3c&H58B4DE&}{a}{\3c&HF9FBFF&}{c}{\3c&H58B4DE&}{k}{\3c&HF9FBFF&}{e}{\3c&H58B4DE&}{r}{\3c&HF9FBFF&}{s}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.48,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{And there.}Và kia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:12.03,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{And the knees!}Đầu gối nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:15.45,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{They sure get tattered quickly \Nwhen you go walking.}Chắc bị rách khi bé đi dạo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:18.34,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Walking? Or hiking on game trails?!}Đi dạo? Chơi game sinh tồn à?
