Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:27.40,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{It may be spring, but it's still chilly.}Tuy mùa xuân nhưng vẫn lạnh quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:30.99,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Sometimes, reality just hits you.}Đôi khi thực tế luôn khắc nghiệt mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:35.15,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Fine. Let's go buy you a new tracksuit.}Thôi, nay đi mua đồ mới nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:38.62,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Yay! Shopping!}Tuyệt vời!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:43.05,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Is it really so exciting?}Có cần phải hào hứng thế không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:47.37,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,Koshitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:49.03,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Ừ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.00,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{By the way...}Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.96,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Where are we?}Ở đây là đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.17,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,Hino!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.76,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{I know that much, you dumbass!}Ai chả biết!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:59.05,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{We were supposed to go straight to the store,}Đáng ra phải đi thẳng tới cửa hàng,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:02.41,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{but we got lost because \Nyou kept making stops!}nhưng lại bị lạc vì cậu cứ vừa đi vừa múa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:08.15,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{But... But I kept seeing really \Ncool sticks to pick up...}N-Nhưng bé thấy mấy cành cây là phải nhặt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:10.90,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{What are you, a grade schooler?!}Học sinh tiểu học à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.55,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Oh, damn it!}Thiệt tình.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:15.90,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{I've done this for 11 episodes, and I still \Ndon't know a damn thing about Hino!}Gần tập cuối rồi mà còn chẳng biết gì về Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:19.94,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Okay. If we go down that hill, \Nwe'll be in the shopping district.}Rồi, leo lên ngọn đồi là trung tâm mua sắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.85,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Come on, let's go.}Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.54,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Er, huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:25.48,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,Shikanoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:26.40,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Where'd you...}Cậu đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.37,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{What are you doing?}Cậu làm trò gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:33.52,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Plastic bottles.}Chai nhựa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:34.52,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:36.13,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Plastic bottles.}Chai nhựa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:39.87,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Ah, right. You're scared of them.}À, cậu sợ chúng nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:42.07,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{I guess that was a plot point somewhere.}Đúng là anime có nói đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:49.61,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Um... Shikanoko?}Shikanoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:52.33,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{There's some behind you, too.}Phía sau cũng có kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.82,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{This is still Nokotan.}Vẫn là Nokotan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:58.82,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\fnTimes New Roman\c&H2A64D6&\pos(490,230.5)}{NB: Nokotan}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.72,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Just how scared are you?}Có gì mà sợ thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:22.25,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{C-Come on. Stand up already.}Nào, đứng lên đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.63,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{We don't really have a choice, \Nso we're taking another way.}Chúng ta sẽ tìm đường khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.68,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{I-I'm the president, remember?}T-Tớ là hội trưởng mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:29.69,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{It's the president's job to take \Ncare of the deer, or something.}Nhiệm vụ của hội trưởng là quan tâm đến nai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:32.85,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Damn it, you sure are a handful, though.}Thiệt tình, cậu phiền ghê đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.87,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Damn it... Whenever I'm with her...}Thiệt tình... cứ hễ ở với cậu ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:47.38,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{I always...}Mình lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:49.23,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{always...}lúc nào cũng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.09,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{get thrown off balance.}bất cẩn cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.72,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Is something wrong?}Có gì hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.09,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{No, it's nothing!}Chẳng có gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.96,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Ah, Koshitan!}A, Koshitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.12,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{We're back where we started.}Chúng ta quay lại chỗ cũ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.22,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Hino is just cursed!}Hino thật đáng nguyền rủa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:17.74,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{There are plastic bottles around every corner!}Có chai nhựa ở khắp mọi nơi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.89,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{How did you even survive this long?}Sao cậu vẫn sống sót đến lúc này vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.55,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Ooh!}Ồ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.55,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{That should take care of things for now.}Tạm thời thế đi đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:38.75,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Well, wearing a tracksuit won't \Nbe against the rules, at least.}Mặc đồng phục thể thao không vi phạm luật mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:41.26,Default,Bashame,0,0,0,,{That's a surprising skill.}Kĩ năng đáng ngạc nhiên đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.65,Default,Anko,0,0,0,,{A former delinquent who's good at sewing...}Một cựu du côn lại giỏi may vá...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:46.26,Default,Anko,0,0,0,,{It's more common than you'd think, \Nbut that's why it's good!}Thật khó tin nhưng không sao, vẫn tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:48.89,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{You want me to literally zip your mouth shut?}Muốn chị may cái này vào mồm không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:52.02,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Thanks, Koshitan! I'll treasure it!}Cảm ơn Koshitan! Bé sẽ giữ gìn nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:55.88,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Sure. I-If it gets ripped again, \NI'll sew it up for you.}Ừm, nếu lỡ rách thì tớ vá lại cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.44,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Yay!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:58.29,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fad(1,325)\fnArial Black\bord2\c&H97544F&\3c&HFFFEFE&\pos(412,190)}{Rip}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:01.69,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{My butt just ripped.}Quần rách mông rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.97,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Come here already.}Lại đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:05.96,Default,Nokotan,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Ùm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:09.55,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs12\bord1\fnArial Black\c&H32282D&\3c&H2967C7&\move(341,200.5,341,334,28,3198)}{Deer Club\N}{\fs8}{Seeking New Club Members}
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.96,0:21:10.01,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{She's a pain in the ass... \Nbut this isn't so bad.}Tuy hơi phiền phức... nhưng cũng không tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:13.51,DefaultItalics,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{I hope these days continue forever.}Hi vọng những ngày này sẽ tiếp diễn mãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:49.98,Default,Girl student A,0,0,0,,{Koshi-san, good morning.}Koshi-san, chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:50.93,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Good morning.}Chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.37,0:23:04.02,Default,Ukai,0,0,0,,{This part and this part will be on the test!}Phần này và phần này sẽ có trong phần kiểm tra.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:06.78,Default,Ukai,0,0,0,,{And this part might not be.}Và phần này thì không.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:15.66,Default,Kohitan,0,0,0,,{Heya.}Xin chào.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:17.53,Default,Anko,0,0,0,,{You're late, Onee-chan.}Chị đến trễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.53,0:23:20.32,Default,Bashame,0,0,0,,{Koshitan-senpai, you're late.}Koshitan, chị đến trễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:23.33,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Well, Shikanoko's been missing all morning.}Cơ mà sáng giờ không thấy Shikanoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.76,0:23:25.84,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Have you guys seen her?}Có ai thấy không?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.41,0:23:27.59,Default,Anko,0,0,0,,{Onee-chan?}Chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.97,0:23:32.22,Default,Bashame,0,0,0,,{Who's Shikanoko?}Shikanoko là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:33.65,Default,Koshitan,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
